- Update the version number in SConstruct
- Update the library version info in src/SConscript
- Update and date ChangeLog
- Update and date NEWS
- Test on several machines
- Run 'scons test' on several machines
- Do a 'fakeroot scons package'
- Unpackage the rest, run 'scons test' on it
- Upload to sourceforge:
  - sftp bmerry@frs.sourceforge.net
  - cd /home/frs/project/bugle/bugle
  - mkdir <release>
  - cd <release>
  - put bugle-<release>.tar.bz2
  - put NEWS README
- Mark as preferred version on sourceforge
- Post details on freecode
- Update project news webpage
- Upload new docs to project webpage
- Tag in svn:
  svn cp svn+ssh://bmerry@svn.code.sf.net/p/bugle/code/trunk svn+ssh://bmerry@svn.code.sf.net/p/bugle/code/tags/release-<version>
- Create new release in trac
